{"name": "okmodule", "metadata": {"name": "okmodule", "version": "1.0.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/lawley0316/okmodule", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "okmodule", "upload_time": 1733994889}, "documentation": ["\n# okmodule: a very simple modular implementation\n\n## Installation\n\n```shell\npip install okmodule\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom okmodule import Module, Command\n\n\nclass MyModule(Module):\n    def __init__(self, x, y):\n        self.x = x\n        self.y = y\n        \n    def main(self):\n        return self.x + self.y\n\n\nclass Blastn(Command):\n    def __init__(self, query, db, out):\n        self.query = query\n        self.db = db\n        self.out = out\n\n    def args(self):\n        return [\n            '-query', self.query,\n            '-db', self.db,\n            '-out', self.out\n        ]\n\n\nmy_module = MyModule(1, 2)\nprint(my_module())\n\nblastn = Blastn('foo', 'bar', 'baz')\nblastn()\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "okmodule", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "okmodule.Module", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "okmodule.Module.name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "okmodule.Module.logger", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "okmodule.Module.log", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "level", "type": null, "default": "...